   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">As part of the standard replacement schedule the following parts
need to be replaced.</p>
      <table class="- topic/table ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Standard Replacement Parts</title>
         <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
            <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="COLSPEC3" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="COLSPEC0" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <thead class="- topic/thead ">
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph id="PartName-16803EA5" class="- topic/ph ">Part Name</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph id="ReplacementCycle-16804135" class="- topic/ph ">Replacement
Cycle</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph id="Notes-168043CF" class="- topic/ph ">Notes</ph>
                  </entry>
               </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
               <row platform="Modular-DC Modular-AC" class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Rectifier modules</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph id="Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph ">Every 8-10 years</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row platform="Modular-Inverter Modular-AC" class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Inverter modules</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph id="Every5-6Years-0253EDCF" class="- topic/ph ">Every 5-6 years</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row platform="Modular-DCDC-Converter" class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">DC/DC Converter modules</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Cabinet fans</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every5-6Years-0253EDCF" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Not all systems have cabinet fans, see <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Parts List</i> or <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Drawings</i>.</ph>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Fan monitoring card</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Not all systems have a fan monitoring card, only systems with cabinet
fans contain a fan monitoring card. See <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Parts List</i> or <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Drawings</i>.</ph>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Surge arrester</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">The replacement cycle depends on quality of the mains. If the alarm
“Surge voltage prot. tripped” is active replace the tripped input
surge arrester immediately.</ph>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Fuses</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Not all systems have fuses, see <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Parts List</i>. Replace immediately
when a fuse has blown or is damaged.</ph>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Power supply
units (PSU)</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Controller</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Includes integrated communication card.</ph>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Display</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph conref="#./Every8-10Years-167EA370" class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Battery</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">See documentation
from the battery manufacturer</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph "/>
                  </entry>
               </row>
